videos.headline: Higdon 50-yard run sets up Patterson TD
videos.description: Karan Higdon breaks off a 50-yard run to set up Shea Patterson for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Penn State TD off blocked FG taken away
videos.description: Penn State's Quinn Nordin blocks Michigan's field goal attempt, but Garrett Taylor's return touchdown is called back because of a penalty.

videos.headline: Penn State fumbles at midfield
videos.description: Trace McSorley fumbles trying to hand the ball off and Chase Winovich recovers for Michigan.

videos.headline: Patterson connects with Peoples-Jones for 23-yard TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson rolls out and finds Donovan Peoples-Jones in the end zone for a 23-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Michigan picks off Penn State backup QB for TD
videos.description: Tommy Stevens throws an interception right to Brandon Watson who returns it 62 yards for a Michigan touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Michigan picks off Penn State backup QB for TD) 2018/11/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: McSorley throws INT deep in own territory
videos.description: Trace McSorley's pass is picked off by David Long who returns it to the Penn State 12-yard line.

videos.headline: Michigan goes up 42-0 with TD run
videos.description: Chris Evans runs up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Penn State gets on the board with rushing TD
videos.description: Tommy Stevens fakes the handoff and runs in for a 8-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Michigan with statement W over Penn State
videos.description: Michigan puts on a clinic against Penn State with Shea Patterson accounting for three touchdowns in a 42-7 rout.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Michigan with statement W over Penn State) 2018/11/3 ESHEET
